  "title": "Facilities & Maintenance Specialist (Taiseng/ 5.25 days)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Carry out routine inspections and maintenance of facility systems, including electrical, air-conditioning, compressed air, and chilled-water systems.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with contractors for scheduled servicing and emergency repairs to ensure smooth and uninterrupted building operations.</li>\n  <li>Oversee vendor activities during renovation works to ensure a smooth and timely transition to newly renovated spaces.</li>\n  <li>Ensure cleanliness and proper upkeep in technical areas such as AHU and switch rooms to maintain equipment efficiency.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate repair and renovation schedules with contractors to achieve cost-effective, high-quality outcomes.</li>\n  <li>Perform hands-on maintenance and repair work related to plumbing, sanitary systems, electrical components, and general facilities upkeep.</li>\n  <li>Troubleshoot and resolve basic telephone line issues as needed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
